result.name: Gaia Vegetarian Restaurant

reviews.text: Good food, very tasty considering that is all made by vegetables. The place is always fully booked. The service staff is very warm.

Went there for dinner and enjoyed all the food. Quality and presentation of the food is good. Service is good. The staff are friendly and smiles back. We've been there for dinner twice already. We're not good in chopsticks, so we asked for a fork. the next time we went, the staff provided a fork straight away. We will definitely go back here.
The food are good and staff are courteous. The environment is far too noisy that you can't hear well what your friends in your table were saying.
Wide variety of vegetarian dishes. The food is tasty and their mock meat taste like the real deal!
Delicious food, I had the mock duck with pancakes, my family members are meat eaters but they all enjoyed their food. Total bill was $520 (HK) for 4 mains and 4 starters.

result.name: 大自然素食

reviews.text: 尖沙咀分店好食😍
味道ok, 太多肉類菜式(雖然用齋製作)，齋口唔齋心，比較擠迫，嘈吵，價錢還可接受
我去個這間，食物很有特色，都幾好食，平日有特價。
環境舒適，食物質素有水準，幾可亂真呀！非常美味𠻹！
價格公道，每道菜份量夠，且色香味俱全，值得推薦。喜歡淡口味的素食者，宜配飯吃。
